* Install as common (perl Makefile.pl ...)

* Activate plugin

Set(@Plugins,(qw(
        RTx::UserSearch
)));


* Add Element to homepage component

Set($HomepageComponents, [qw(
	QuickCreate
	Quicksearch
	MyAdminQueues
	MySupportQueues
	MyReminders
	RefreshHomepage
	Dashboards
	SavedSearches
	RTx-UserSearch
)]);

* Restart RT and check you have the right 'ShowUserSearch'. Only
with this right the box will be displayed
